snippet.title: Emergency Ambulance Simulator - Trailer
snippet.description: Emergency Ambulance Simulator lets you feel the rush of getting to an accident as soon as possible to save someone who has been injured. Brought to you by Astragon and published by Excalibur Publishing's Extra play range, players speed through the streets to make sure that they get patients to the hospital in time. Sometimes, you will be required to treat the patient before taking them to the hospital. Out on the 24th of February at a great RRP of £9.99
